# Fashion, Home + Interiors (FHI) Metallic Shimmers Color Guide

## Add brilliance and drama to any design

Sku#: FHIP310B

$ 167.00

Add To Cart

Expand Pantone’s Fashion, Home + Interiors (FHI) palette with 200 new luxurious metallic finishes, in one handheld guide. This carefully selected collection of trend-driven metallic colors is an ideal tool for designers to get inspiration and specify metallic effects for fashion accessories, footwear, electronics, housewares, and interiors.

- A trend-driven selection of metallics to broaden and compliment Pantone’s [FHI System](https://www.pantone.com/color-systems-fashion "Click to Learn More about Pantone's Fashion, Home + Interiors Color System")
- Metallics add premium impact to designs for products and interiors
- TPM (Textile Paper–Metallic) format offers a brighter and lighter sparkle
- Fan-format guide displays one full-bleed color per page

